author: news@courierpublicationsllc.com (Staff)
title: MoJO plays Great Gatsby Party
text:
MoJO plays Great Gatsby Party Oct 20, 2015 Mondaynite Jazz Orchestra 
Rockland â€” The Speakeasy, 2 Park Drive, will return to its flapper-era roots Friday, Oct. 30, with the Great Gatsby Party starting 8:30 p.m. Admission is $5. Everyone is encouraged to dress like a (19)20-something and kick up their heels in style. 
Fueling the dance floor will be the Mondaynite Jazz Orchestra, also known as MoJO. The 18-piece big band plays an extraordinary mix of modern and traditional jazz. 
For Halloween, local rockers Dolphin Strikers will play the Speakeasy starting around 9 p.m. Saturday, Oct. 31.
